You are helping me build Mastrify.

Rules:
- Do not rewrite working systems unnecessarily
- Fix one issue at a time
- Preserve existing UI and design
- Preserve audio preview and A/B toggle logic
- Preserve middleware behavior
- Always explain which files are being changed
- Prefer minimal fixes over large rewrites
- Frontend uses Next.js/React/Tailwind
- Backend uses Node.js/Express/ffmpeg
- Backend usually runs on localhost:3002
- Frontend usually runs on localhost:3000